# This project uses Doppler for secrets management.
# No .env file needed — secrets are injected at runtime via `doppler run`.
#
# Setup:
#   1. Install Doppler CLI: https://docs.doppler.com/docs/install-cli
#   2. doppler login
#   3. doppler setup  (select your project/config)
#   4. doppler secrets set JIRA_BASE_URL=https://yoursite.atlassian.net
#   5. doppler secrets set JIRA_EMAIL=your-email@example.com
#   6. doppler secrets set JIRA_API_TOKEN=your-api-token
#
# Required secrets:
#   JIRA_BASE_URL   - e.g., https://yoursite.atlassian.net
#   JIRA_EMAIL      - your Jira account email
#   JIRA_API_TOKEN  - API token from https://id.atlassian.com/manage-profile/security/api-tokens
